snippet.title: State of Emergency 2 - Full Game Longplay Walkthrough [PS2 Gameplay]
snippet.description:
Full longplay / playthrough of the game State of Emergency 2 (no commentaries). State of Emergency was released by DC Studios in 2006 for Playstation 2. PS2 version emulated with PCSX2.
Support the channel on Patreon: https://www.patreon.com/neogamertvga
